      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair overall condition and would make a reliable daily driver or a great project car for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the cabin is intact but shows clear signs of use, including some wear on the driver's seat bolster and a few minor stains in the carpet. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it will likely need some routine suspension work and a fresh set of tires in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car that has been used regularly, offered at a price that reflects its current state.",
