      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for this diamond in the rough! This vehicle is in poor condition and will need some dedicated mechanical attention and cosmetic repairs to get back to its best, but it offers a fantastic opportunity for a project lover or someone looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper. It's sold as-is and ready for a fresh start with a new owner who sees its potential!",
