    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is very sound; the engine runs strong, the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and the suspension provides a comfortable ride. The interior is clean with only minor signs of use, and all electronic features, including the climate control and infotainment system, are fully operational. While the exterior looks great overall, there are a few minor paint chips and light scratches consistent with careful daily use. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that is ready for its next owner.",
