    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a showroom-quality vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously maintained, stored in a climate-controlled garage, and treated with the utmost care. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish with no chips, swirls, or imperfections, protected by a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, with supple leather seats that show zero wear, that unmistakable 'new car' scent, and every electronic feature functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; it comes with a comprehensive service record, brand-new performance tires, and an engine bay that is spotless. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom car cover. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a perfect example of this model.",
